                           <note>Magic prayer agains demons and evel eye.</note>
                        </item>

                        <item xml:id="a2">
                          <locus target="#1r"/>
                           <desc type="GuestText">
                              <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2332serata">Śǝrʿāta beta krǝstiyān</title></desc>
                            <q xml:lang="am">ማገሩ፡ እንደዥማቸውነው፨ ሣእሩ፡ እንደ፡ ሥጋቸው፡ በተናኘ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ እግዚእትነ፡ ማርያም፡
                              ኘች፡ ምስሶው፨ </q>
                              <note>One of the texts known as Sǝrʿata beta krǝstiyān.</note>
                        </item>

                        <item xml:id="e1">
                          <desc>A notice written on a piece of paper placed in the volume,
                             indicating the name of the seller and the date of purchase.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="greek"> Ἠγοράσϑη ἀπό τοῦ ἀβυσσινοῦ Δανιὴλ Besunech, ἐν Ἱερουσολύμοις 1888 μαΐου 3.
                           </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">It has been purchased from an Abyssinian
                             <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12386DanielBezunah">Dānǝʾel Bǝzunah </persName>
                            in <placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1218">Jerusalem</placeName>,
                             on <date>3 May 1888</date>.</q>
                        </item>

                     </list>
